Ajai Sanders https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ajai_Sanders 0 Ajai Sanders (born Angela Marie Wilson; April 24, 1967) is an American actress and stand-up comedian, best known for her supporting role as Gina Deveaux in the sitcom A Different World from 1991 until the series original ending in 1993. Sanders is sometimes credited as Ajai Richards.
